snippet: The Ferguson police officer who fatally shot 18-year-old Michael Brown resigned Saturday, and protests intensified in the St. Louis suburb where violence erupted earlier this week when a grand jury decided not to indict him....

headline.print_headline: Officer Who Shot Michael Brown Resigns in Ferguson
headline.main: Officer Who Shot Michael Brown Resigns in Ferguson

lead_paragraph: The Ferguson police officer who fatally shot 18-year-old Michael Brown resigned Saturday, and protests intensified in the St. Louis suburb where violence erupted earlier this week when a grand jury decided not to indict him.
